{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use four-dimensional thinking to control time and navigate through the world of <strong>Beta MAX</strong>. This atmospheric first-person puzzle platformer takes you on a journey with Max, who has been thrust into a retro-futuristic 80's inspired world full of increasingly complex puzzles.<br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/Gameplay_1.gif?t=1732262555\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>You Will</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Pause and rewind time </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Manoeuvre objects onto floor switches and remotely activate wall switches </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Utilise time chambers and velocity accelerators </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Dodge lasers and avoid crushers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Travel on moving platforms and traverse fragmenting bridges </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/Gameplay_2.gif?t=1732262555\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>On Each Level</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Find the hidden collectible </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Overcome all obstacles to complete without errors </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Move with speed and precision to get under par-time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/Crushers.gif?t=1732262555\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Yoink!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2216250/34ce1d05cdde2dfb49ee1d4ae12a3b4e58c22320.jpg"},{"name":"Punctual","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2216250/a544812143966726cdf12cf3531eedb9ee1ce6fb.